items.title: Elon Musk and Vivek Ramaswamy meet with Republicans on Capitol Hill | REUTERS
items.author: Reuters
items.content:
Billionaire Elon Musk and former presidential candidate Vivek Ramaswamy met with Republican lawmakers whose support they will need to win the sweeping spending cuts that 
President-elect Donald Trump has asked them to find.

Ahead of the meeting Speaker of the House Mike Johnson criticized the Biden administration for what he described as reckless spending in its final months.

items.title: LIVE: South Korean President and ruling party leader expected to arrive at the parliament | reuters
items.author: Reuters
items.content:
South Korean President Yoon Suk Yeol and ruling party leader Han Dong-hoon are expected to arrive at the parliament after their meeting over martial law.

The party leader said President Yoon needs to be removed from power for trying to impose martial law, as the government denied reports that it was preparing to issue another martial law declaration.
